


• Consist of at least 5 questions
• Be multiple choice (1, 2, 3, 4 - A, B, C, D etc.)
• Handle an incorrect input (5, E, a, etc.)
• Award a user 5 points for a correct answer
• Remove 2 points for an incorrect answer
• Show the total at the end with a relevant message

